{"tid":214656,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司俾員工\"選擇\"供唔供強積金係咪犯法？","createTime":"2017-04-24T01:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T03:41:04.000Z","uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b835fce6a708b0c9d5c5a7310fccfc8c40e3f52","tid":214656,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"對上一份工<br />\n返左一個星期後個老闆就問我供唔供強積金<br />\n我問有得唔供架咩<br />\n佢話唔供就可以出糧出多幾百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底公司有無權咁樣俾員工選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998c7e18fe4ad6fc82648b515537024b4f94ed0a","tid":214656,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:01:51.000Z","msg":"有公積金就ok la"},{"pid":"d54b871c3e4e460a4b0d64a523681b8e8ea5a798","tid":214656,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有公積金就ok la</blockquote><br />\n咩金都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現金出糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f52951facaa4b99e4076a80a0d0e67e1f158ee","tid":214656,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:03:02.000Z","msg":"你選擇唔供，你同你老細經已犯法<br />\n不過老細扣左5%又無同你供，只係佢犯法"},{"pid":"81b0ba13e269595a16d73fd4b6c3f1b7fd31fce2","tid":214656,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"當然係冇，佢所謂嘅出多幾百筆糧，<br />\n我相信只係僱員嗰5%，<br />\n即係佢想慳僱主要供嗰5%。<br />\n<br />\n除非你公司有更佳嘅公積金計劃，<br />\n如果唔係你老細都係度縮，辭職吧。"},{"pid":"5b2b01886dd737c6a1039b66ba8df425b4aad30e","tid":214656,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:04:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaec4ac5ec6423f5dea11edbcad3c528bb6764f9","tid":214656,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"炒散就自己負責供"},{"pid":"4830f7f1f0fe53a10